Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.38,0:00:05.58,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューン卿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.41,0:00:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Daryun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.48,0:00:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The second prince of the kingdom sindoor, Rajendra
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.74,0:00:12.74,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,俺はシンドゥラ国と俺の命運を　お主に委ねることにした
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.75,0:00:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I have decided to entrust your fate,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.63,0:00:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and his kingdom sindoor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.46,0:00:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you take for this assignment?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.50,0:00:16.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,快く引き受けてもらえないだろうか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.93,0:00:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,it is difficult for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.98,0:00:18.50,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,迷惑ですな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.02,0:00:21.92,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか　ダリューン卿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.17,0:00:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Daryun, do not tell me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.32,0:00:25.76,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,決闘に勝つ自信が　ないというのではあるまいな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.68,0:00:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that you are not sure of their victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.19,0:00:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You can interpret it as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.26,0:00:27.92,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ご解釈は　お好きなように
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.31,0:00:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But I serve the Prince Arslan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.34,0:00:30.44,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,私はアルスラーン殿下の臣下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.98,0:00:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Without his order
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.02,0:00:32.98,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下のご命令がないかぎり
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.19,0:00:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not agree on anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.26,0:00:35.59,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,どのような御用も　お引き受けできぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.58,0:00:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I can not let Gadevi to seize my sindoor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.60,0:00:44.84,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,我がシンドゥラをガーデーヴィの好きにさせるわけにはいかない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.12,0:00:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps this request is selfish, but ...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.14,0:00:47.16,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,身勝手な話かもしれないが…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:48.60,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,アルスラーン殿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.50,0:00:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Lion,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.61,0:00:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.68,0:00:51.96,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,どうか俺に力を貸してくれぬか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.38,0:00:53.94,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あぁ…　いや…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.89,0:00:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.72,0:00:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.72,0:00:58.06,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,分かりました
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.30,0:01:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If it helps put an end to your quarrel ...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.34,0:01:01.62,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,それで　このいさかいを止めることができるのでしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.06,0:01:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Darjun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.08,0:01:04.76,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューン
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.85,0:01:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I can ask you to do this?
