Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.97,0:01:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the subjects of the kingdom confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.02,0:01:10.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,臣民も　うろたえている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.74,0:01:14.80,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,カリカーラ王としては　苦肉の決断でしょうな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.77,0:01:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,For King Karikaly, it must be a solution - the last hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.74,0:01:18.30,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,お願いいたす
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.76,0:01:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.38,0:01:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince.
