Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.92,0:03:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Participate in the fight before the gods ... huge responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.92,0:03:24.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,神前決闘とは　責任重大だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.49,0:03:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt that by Gadevi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.52,0:03:31.02,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ガーデーヴィ勢から　俺より手練れの戦士を用意できるとは思えんがな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,perform more skilled warrior than I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.33,0:03:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You got me has encouraged.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.36,0:03:34.02,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,頼もしいかぎりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.39,0:03:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:37.98,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし　ガーデーヴィは奸計もいとわぬだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.42,0:03:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Gadevi not disdain, and in a roundabout way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.29,0:03:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.34,0:03:39.46,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,油断はできぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.13,0:03:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a small detour -
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.18,0:03:43.70,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,これしきの寄り道　大事の前の小事だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.04,0:03:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,it is a trifle compared with the important task.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.42,0:03:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is necessary to go around,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.48,0:03:46.78,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,確かに寄り道になってしまったが
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.93,0:03:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but you might think differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:48.66,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,こうも考えられるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.26,0:03:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as this issue will be resolved,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.32,0:03:54.60,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,この一件が片づけば　アルスラーン殿下の名声が広まり
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.11,0:03:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone will know about the noble Prince Arslan,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.98,0:03:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and in the future it will be to our advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:57.50,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,我々にとっては　今後の得になる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.02,0:04:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Our uprising of Peshavarda also contribute to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.08,0:04:01.86,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ペシャワールからの蜂起も　より強固なものにできるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.07,0:04:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the more I can not lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.12,0:04:05.68,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,であれば　なおのこと　負けるわけにはいかぬな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.53,0:04:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,On the day when Bachmann overshadowed Prince,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.54,0:04:09.80,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,バフマン殿が殿下をかばった日
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.03,0:04:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I remembered the words of his uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.08,0:04:11.70,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,伯父の言葉を考えた
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why he entrusted me with the prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:14.68,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ殿下を俺に託したのか…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.30,0:04:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever its origin,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:18.56,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下の出自がどうであろうと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.04,0:04:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,my host - Prince Arslan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.06,0:04:21.98,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の主君は　アルスラーン殿下だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kingdom sindoor Royal Capital Uraiyur
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.43,0:04:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.44,0:04:34.24,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This knight in black will represent Rajendra ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:38.74,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あの黒衣の騎士がラジェンドラの代理人だと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.35,0:04:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A duel that will determine the fate of sindoor,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:44.40,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,シンドゥラの運命を決める戦いに　パルス人を選ぶとは…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.48,0:04:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,he chose parsiantsa ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.07,0:04:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is a cynical smart aleck!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:47.96,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あの恥知らずめ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.38,0:04:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of this, the black knight
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.44,0:04:53.84,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,黒衣の騎士の強さは　国を越えて　誰もが認めるところ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.41,0:04:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,recognized by all, no matter where they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.88,0:04:56.74,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,急ぎ　我が軍の中から人選を
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.91,0:04:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to quickly pick someone from you ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.54,0:05:03.20,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤツの鎖を解け
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.59,0:05:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Release him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.42,0:05:04.18,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,First Prince sindoor, Gadevi
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.63,0:05:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I said release Bahadur!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.68,0:05:08.90,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,バハードゥルの鎖を解くのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hereditary Grand Vizier kingdom sindoor, Mahendra
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.01,0:05:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Baxadura?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.02,0:05:11.40,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,バハードゥルを
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.70,0:05:12.88,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤツは危険です
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.88,0:05:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And who else can defeat this man ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.92,0:05:16.36,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,では　ヤツ以外で　あの男に勝てる者がいるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.77,0:05:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They forced me to entrust the fate of wild animal ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.78,0:05:22.56,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,野獣に運命を委ねなくてはならないとは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Just disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.28,0:05:24.76,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,浅ましいことよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.36,0:05:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.46,0:05:27.80,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,だが　やむをえぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.68,0:06:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems we are not particularly happy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:06:01.14,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あまり歓迎されていないようだな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In the first place, the aliens have rarely here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:04.84,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そもそも　よその国の人間が珍しいんだろうね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.41,0:06:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like at the festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:21.98,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,お祭りみたいだね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.08,0:06:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not here for fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.08,0:06:23.62,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,遊びじゃないんだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.78,0:06:25.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,分かってるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.88,0:06:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.39,0:06:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I was waiting for you, Prince Arslan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.42,0:06:29.76,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,お待ちしておりました
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.38,0:06:31.68,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,アルスラーン殿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.34,0:06:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be a witness to the moment when you become king.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.36,0:06:37.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,貴殿が王となる瞬間を　この目で　しかと見させていただきます
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Much obliged.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:39.86,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,深く感謝いたします
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.19,0:06:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my father, the king Karikal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.22,0:06:43.58,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,我が父　カリカーラ王です
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruler sindoor kingdom, Karikal II
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.91,0:07:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince, is now verified your majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.96,0:07:05.80,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下　威厳が試される場所です
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.25,0:07:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you do not like it, but ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:08.24,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,本意ではないかもしれませんが…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.08,0:07:12.88,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,分かっている
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.13,0:07:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.78,0:07:25.80,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:27.16,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いや
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.48,0:07:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.65,0:07:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one of these ambitious men blessed by the gods sindoor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.68,0:07:31.64,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,シンドゥラの神々が　どちらの野心家を　ひいきするのか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.24,0:07:33.52,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,見ものじゃな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.52,0:07:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be interesting to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This ... Knight Parsis ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:50.78,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あれが… パルスの騎士…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Warrior Parsis, a spokesman Rajendra, Daryun
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Warrior sindoor representative Gadevi, Bahadur
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Warrior Parsis?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:22.96,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,パルスの戦士か
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.20,0:08:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you have fun to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.28,0:08:26.48,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,楽しませろよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.34,0:08:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If you will die soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.38,0:08:32.68,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,すぐに死んだら　つまらない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.18,0:08:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:41.46,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,何あれ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.06,0:08:46.22,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ラジェンドラ殿　あのバハードゥルという男は何者です
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Rajendra, who is this man named Bahadur?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.68,0:08:48.44,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,心配なされるな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Daryunu he is no match.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:50.90,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューン卿には　到底　及ばぬよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:08:58.80,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫です　殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.32,0:08:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All will be well, Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.04,0:09:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Daryun can not lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.06,0:09:01.26,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューン様が　負けるはずありません
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.53,0:09:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the greatest hero on this earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:04.56,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あの方は　地上で　いちばんの勇者なのですから
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.84,0:09:16.20,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,これより　シンドゥラ次期国王位を賭けて　神前決闘を行う
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.91,0:09:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We begin to fight, which determines the heir to the throne sindoor
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.17,0:09:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the gods!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.64,0:09:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The outcome of this fight is sacred and inviolable,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.66,0:09:20.20,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,この結果は神聖にして不可侵なるものなれば
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.29,0:09:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and neither party shall have no right to challenge it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.36,0:09:23.78,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,両者とも異を唱えることあるべからず
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.15,0:09:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So we began!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.18,0:09:30.70,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,では　始めよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.68,0:10:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Slightly hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.70,0:10:12.70,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,浅かったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.46,0:10:20.78,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あれは人間ではないな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.16,0:10:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Animal wearing the mask of people can be found everywhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.86,0:10:24.88,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,人の皮をかぶった　獣はどこにでもいるが
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.08,0:10:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but it is truly a wild animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.08,0:10:27.24,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あれは　まさしく猛獣じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.84,0:10:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Daryun not lose another person, but ...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.86,0:10:31.16,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューン卿は　人間相手なら　負けるはずもないが…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.81,0:10:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Darjun ...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.84,0:10:39.68,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューン…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.57,0:11:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Darjun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:06.42,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューン
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:11.62,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殺れ　バハードゥル
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.01,0:11:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobey, Bahadur!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Will cut this knight into pieces
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.80,0:11:13.58,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,その騎士を八つ裂きにし
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.67,0:11:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and force these silly parsiantsev regret that they dared to go so far!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.70,0:11:18.22,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,愚かなパルス人どもに　ここまで出向いたことを後悔させてやるのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.28,0:11:33.36,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューン様…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.31,0:11:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Daryun ...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.58,0:11:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It turned out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:51.78,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,やった
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.78,0:12:13.72,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューン
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.82,0:12:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Darjun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.00,0:12:28.80,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いいぞ　バハードゥル　その調子だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for you, Bahadur! That's the spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.50,0:12:33.12,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,忌々しいパルスの犬めを　早く葬るのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.54,0:12:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Send this hellish hound Parsis into oblivion!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:34.94,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,聞いたことがある
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.88,0:12:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard about it ...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.66,0:12:37.96,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あの男は　サメと同じだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.71,0:12:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This person is almost like a shark.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.16,0:12:40.56,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,痛みを感じるということがないのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.19,0:12:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He is completely immune to pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.80,0:12:42.68,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな人間がありうると
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Such people exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.38,0:12:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:48.14,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたは　それを知っていて
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You!..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.96,0:12:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.30,0:12:50.94,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューンを神前決闘の代理人に選んだのか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.34,0:12:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Daryuna and chose as its representative in the match before the gods ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.14,0:12:52.52,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,アルスラーン殿…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.26,0:12:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Lion ...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.77,0:12:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If this monster kill Daryuna ...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.82,0:12:55.62,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,もし　ダリューンが　あの怪物に殺されでもしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.42,0:12:58.46,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,パルスの神々に誓って
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.48,0:12:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,By the gods Parsis,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.86,0:13:03.36,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あの怪物とあなたの首を並べて　ここの城門に掛けてやる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:13:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I will take thee, and the monster's head
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.27,0:13:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and hang them here on the gates of the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.36,0:13:07.40,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,落ち着きなされ　パルスのお客人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.48,0:13:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Please calm down, a guest from the Parsis.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:13.74,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ガーデーヴィがバハードゥルを選んだのは
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.65,0:13:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Gadevi Bahadur chose to fight already, after Rajendra made his choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:16.84,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ラジェンドラよりあとのことじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard your man - a hero without equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.48,0:13:21.36,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,お客人の部下は無双の勇者とか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.96,0:13:26.62,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ガーデーヴィとて考えあぐね　牢より解き放った
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.00,0:13:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And in desperation, Gadevi decided to release this man from prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:33.24,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,それほど敵から恐れられる部下を　信じておやりなされ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.42,0:13:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So, so afraid of the enemies of your subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.25,0:13:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to believe in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.64,0:13:41.88,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ラジェンドラ　覚悟を決めておいた方がよさそうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.77,0:13:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Rajendra, it seems that you should be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.72,0:13:47.72,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,父上　パルスの王太子などと言いながら　あの取り乱しよう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.77,0:13:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, he says, that is the Crown Prince of Parsis,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.07,0:13:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and so it breaks down ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.14,0:13:50.14,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,見苦しいことでございますな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.20,0:13:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's such a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.50,0:13:52.06,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ガーデーヴィよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.65,0:13:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Gadevi,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.32,0:13:58.40,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,もし　そなたがこのパルスの王子のせめて半分でもよい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,if you are at least half-worried about his people so
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:14:02.40,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,部下を大事に思う人間であったら
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.08,0:14:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,both of them worried that Prince Parsis,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.54,0:14:07.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,わしは　そなたを　とっくに　王太子に定めていたであろう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.67,0:14:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,you would have already become crown prince here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.12,0:14:11.42,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,心得ております　父上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.17,0:14:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:15.32,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,だとよいのだがな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.14,0:14:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:19.78,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ　バハードゥル　そろそろ　決着をつけろ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So Bahadur, it is time to put an end to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.70,0:14:26.54,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なんちゅう力だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.83,0:14:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What is his strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.90,0:14:30.88,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューン様
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Daryun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:36.82,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そろそろ終わりです
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.12,0:14:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.10,0:14:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.10,0:14:47.86,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,今だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.10,0:14:58.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,何をやっておる　バハードゥル
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.23,0:14:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Bahadur ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.34,0:15:00.34,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,また　牢に戻りたいか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:15:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted back to jail ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:14.16,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,覚悟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.21,0:15:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.98,0:15:30.34,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,短剣だと…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.05,0:15:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Short sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.88,0:15:34.24,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,折れた長剣以外に武器がないように見せかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.01,0:15:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,By doing so, as if he had a weapon was only a broken sword,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.54,0:15:36.80,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,敵の油断を待っていたのです
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.55,0:15:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He waited until the enemy will lose vigilance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.51,0:15:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He's pretty good tactics.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:40.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤツも　なかなか　策士ですね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.43,0:15:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In ...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.44,0:15:42.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリュ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:43.06,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,それまで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.06,0:15:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:48.48,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューンの勝ち
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Daryun won.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.72,0:15:52.96,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,すなわち　ラジェンドラの勝利じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.82,0:15:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, the winner Rajendra.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:15:59.66,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ラジェンドラ様
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.28,0:15:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Rajendra!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.92,0:16:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Our new king!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.00,0:16:00.34,UP JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,新しき国王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.36,0:16:01.48,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ラジェンドラ様
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.41,0:16:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Rajendra!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.20,0:16:05.48,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,やったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.25,0:16:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:06.98,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,さすが　ダリューン様
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.62,0:16:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our Mr. Daryun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.16,0:16:12.26,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューン…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.17,0:16:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Darjun ...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:17.98,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.47,0:16:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.68,0:16:19.66,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.92,0:16:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.60,0:16:21.74,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,認めん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.90,0:16:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not agree!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:24.24,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,み…　認めんぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.39,0:16:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not accept ...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.90,0:16:28.34,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな不当な裁きに　誰が従うものか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.98,0:16:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This unjust decision ...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Who will follow him ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:33.22,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ガーデーヴィ　神々の裁きに対して　異を唱えるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.99,0:16:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Gadevi you intend to oppose the decision of the gods ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.84,0:16:36.38,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,愚弟が　神々が…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.90,0:16:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn brother ... Gods ...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:39.96,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ　神々が間違っているのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.94,0:16:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! It is the gods are mistaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.06,0:16:44.14,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あの王子様　今頃　気付いたらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.13,0:16:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that the prince is too late noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.37,0:16:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The gods are wrong all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:46.58,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,神々は　いつだって間違うし
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.75,0:16:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and their errors are reflected in us humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.78,0:16:50.02,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,間違った結果を人間に押しつけるものさ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:52.16,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ガーデーヴィよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.92,0:16:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Gadevi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:57.12,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,父上　私に王位をお譲りください
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.92,0:16:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, give me the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:59.28,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,この剣に懸けて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:16:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear by this sword ...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.46,0:17:00.94,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,血迷ったか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.71,0:17:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You crazy ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:06.04,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様が出過ぎたまねをしなければ　こんなことには…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.22,0:17:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had not encroached on more than you should,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.43,0:17:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,this would have happened ...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.82,0:17:07.84,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,親衛隊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.95,0:17:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Strajnïkï!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.24,0:17:09.82,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ラジェンドラを殺せ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.44,0:17:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Rajendra kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.98,0:17:12.16,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,この者たちこそが謀反人である
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.18,0:17:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They are the real traitors!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.40,0:17:14.82,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,王をお守りしろ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.44,0:17:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Protect the King!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.94,0:17:18.56,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ガーデーヴィを討て
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.07,0:17:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Push Gadevi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.40,0:17:20.98,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ラジェンドラを殺せ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Rajendra kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.04,0:17:33.72,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,これ以上は当事者たちの問題ですな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.21,0:17:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Then a solution has to stakeholders.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:36.54,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下　巻き込まれてはなりませぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.17,0:17:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince, we should not interfere in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:42.24,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ナルサス様
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.33,0:17:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Narsus!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.94,0:17:46.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,このっ　あんたたちのために来てあげたんでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.90,0:17:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We came here for your sake, forget ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.52,0:17:48.46,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ギーヴ　ファランギース殿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Giev! Gospoƶa Farangis!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.82,0:17:50.24,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下　こちらへ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.89,0:17:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.72,0:17:53.96,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,やれやれ　言わんこっちゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.85,0:17:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee. What did I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.14,0:17:55.86,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,パルスの一味を捕らえろ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.27,0:17:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Seize the conspirators of the Parsis!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.02,0:17:58.58,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,この者ら　ラジェンドラの間者なるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.07,0:17:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Rajendra spies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.06,0:18:00.38,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,言いがかりじゃな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.11,0:18:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Bold accusation!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.44,0:18:05.66,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下やダリューン卿を　巻き込んでおいて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.44,0:18:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of them, the prince and Daryun were involved in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.94,0:18:07.60,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なんと身勝手な連中じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.95,0:18:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Selfish bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.90,0:18:11.23,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あの第一王子　まさか負けるなどとは
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.12,0:18:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This first Prince did not seem to even think that to lose, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.23,0:18:13.54,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,夢にも思っていなかったんでしょうな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.26,0:18:16.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,どけ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.42,0:18:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,From the road!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.60,0:18:18.48,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.76,0:18:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:29.38,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,こちらです
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.68,0:18:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:32.54,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ジャスワント　お主…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Jaswant! You...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.58,0:18:34.50,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,これは　シンドゥラ内のいさかい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.60,0:18:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a battle between sinduriantsami.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.72,0:18:38.38,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,神前決闘の日に　他国の王族に非礼があったとなれば
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.73,0:18:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If the day of the fight of the gods
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.27,0:18:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the royal family of another kingdom will suffer,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:40.14,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,国の恥となります
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.69,0:18:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This disgrace our kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.86,0:18:42.68,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,私を助けてくれるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.88,0:18:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're helping me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.22,0:18:50.72,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,何をやっておる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.54,0:18:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.16,0:18:53.68,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,父上を　あの愚弟より取り返せ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.21,0:18:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Take away from this stupid father's brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.28,0:18:59.44,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ガーデーヴィ様　私どもの負けにございます
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.34,0:18:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Gadevi, we were defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.78,0:19:02.72,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様…　私の意に背くのか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.88,0:19:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! .. You will argue with me ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.18,0:19:09.24,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,神前決闘の結果に異議を唱えるとは　あってはならぬことです
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.26,0:19:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Deny the outcome of the match to the gods
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.22,0:19:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,is not allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.68,0:19:13.34,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,どうか　覚悟をお決めなさいませ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.81,0:19:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.23,0:19:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,find the strength to accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.62,0:19:16.90,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,さては　貴様… 寝返ったな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So, over to the other side!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.96,0:19:20.74,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ラジェンドラの犬めと　裏でどんな取り引きをしたのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.02,0:19:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of deal you made with this dog Rajendra behind my back ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.00,0:19:23.06,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下　何をおっしゃいます
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.11,0:19:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince, you say ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.40,0:19:25.12,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,国王陛下の御前ですぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We are in front of His Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.16,0:19:27.84,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,やかましい　私は認めぬぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.25,0:19:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence! I will not accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:31.16,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下　ここはラジェンドラ殿下に頭を下げ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.09,0:19:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince, is now better to bow to the prince Rajendra ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.08,0:19:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.16,0:19:32.26,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,黙れ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.84,0:19:41.36,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,マヘーンドラ様…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.89,0:19:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Mahendra ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.68,0:19:42.94,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,宰相閣下…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Great vizier ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.18,0:19:44.54,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,おじけづきよって
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.22,0:19:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you to retreat ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.00,0:19:48.66,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした　親衛隊　謀反人どもを皆殺しにしろ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.01,0:19:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The guards, than you are engaged ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.78,0:19:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill all traitors to the last!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.34,0:19:51.50,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした　早く捕らえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.35,0:19:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Alive! Destroy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.98,0:19:54.32,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,剣を収めよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.06,0:19:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Remove the swords!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.22,0:20:00.80,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,この戦いは　お主らの国の行く末を決める神聖なものではなかったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.23,0:19:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is not this the holy fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.73,0:20:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,determines the fate of your kingdom ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.44,0:20:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is dissatisfied with something, let challenges me, and fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.44,0:20:05.34,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,不服ある者は　今ここで俺に勝負を挑め
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.46,0:20:14.34,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ショラ·セーナニー…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Cher Senate ...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.68,0:20:16.06,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ショラ·セーナニー
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.71,0:20:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Cher Senate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.71,0:20:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Note .: Cher Senani means "ferocious tiger-general."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.42,0:20:20.04,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ショラ·セーナニー　ショラ·セーナニー
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.46,0:20:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Cher Senate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.61,0:20:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Cher Senate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.44,0:20:23.92,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ショラ·セーナニー　ショラ·セーナニー
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.53,0:20:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Cher Senate! Cher Senate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.34,0:20:27.40,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ショラ·セーナニー　ショラ·セーナニー
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.98,0:20:30.12,UP JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,皆の者　静まれ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.05,0:20:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, everyone shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.92,0:20:31.76,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ショラ·セーナニー
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:37.70,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ガーデーヴィは神意と勅命　共に背いた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.06,0:20:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Gadevi opposes the will of the gods and the king's orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.48,0:20:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever follows him will be considered an accomplice in treason!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.48,0:20:43.72,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤツに従う者は　大逆罪の共犯とする
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.58,0:20:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.38,0:20:48.64,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだ　お前たち
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.02,0:20:50.72,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ　俺の言うことを聞かん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.13,0:20:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you not listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.16,0:20:52.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,戦え
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.28,0:20:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.26,0:20:55.06,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,兄上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.41,0:20:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.82,0:20:59.38,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　大罪人ガーデーヴィ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.87,0:20:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather criminal Gadevi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:01.48,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,捕らえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.96,0:21:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Grab!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.10,0:21:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.10,0:21:05.90,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,こら　放せ　貴様ら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes you!..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.98,0:21:14.20,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,マヘーンドラ様
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.10,0:21:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Mahendra!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.56,0:21:19.58,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,マヘーンドラ様…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.69,0:21:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Mahenrda ...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.84,0:21:27.26,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ジャスワントか…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.93,0:21:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Jaswant?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.20,0:21:33.34,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,マヘーンドラ様
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.20,0:21:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Mahendra!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.76,0:21:37.76,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,悲しむな　ジャスワント…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.79,0:21:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not worry, Jaswant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.86,0:21:40.98,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,惜しむ必要はない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.92,0:21:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to mourn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.30,0:21:45.46,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,わしは仕える主君を誤った
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.34,0:21:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I just chose the wrong master.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.46,0:21:50.68,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,愚か者にふさわしい最期だ…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.55,0:21:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A fitting end for the gander.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.84,0:21:52.40,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,何をおっしゃいます
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.93,0:21:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.78,0:22:02.60,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,お前には何も報いてやれなかった…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.80,0:22:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I could not ... repay you ... nothing ...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.90,0:22:05.02,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ジャスワント…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.99,0:22:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Jaswant, please,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.82,0:22:09.84,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は　道を違えるな…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.69,0:22:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,not set foot on a curve track ...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.17,0:22:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,YakuSub Studio
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.11,0:22:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,kimi ga deatta kokoro wa kitto
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.11,0:22:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All the souls that you could meet on the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.12,0:22:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,translation Mu_Cool
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.90,0:22:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,hitotsu datte machigai janai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.90,0:22:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,certainly it was pure and innocent,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.12,0:22:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Editorial Mu_Cool
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.08,0:22:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,onaji yume wo daite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.08,0:22:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We kept the same dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.25,0:22:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Making Helge
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.30,0:22:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,michi wo tagaeta hito wo omotta
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.30,0:22:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,People walking different paths,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.75,0:22:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,nozarashi no akogare wo kakagete susumu kouya
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.75,0:22:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,killed all my hopes and desires revive again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.51,0:23:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,hohoemi mo sono namida mo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.51,0:23:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Smile on his face, tears running down her cheeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.22,0:23:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,koko ni suteteyukenai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.22,0:23:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to go ahead, they should not be forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.28,0:23:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,kage wo daite shiroku takaku
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.28,0:23:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Covered by the shadow of the summer, so white and immense,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.39,0:23:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,namonaki boku to kimi no hata
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.39,0:23:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,our with you nameless flag flies.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.66,0:23:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,mada hatenaku tsudzuku kono mich ino kanata ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.66,0:23:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There, on the road, which extends an endless path,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.53,0:23:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,tatta hitotsu no hikari wo sen no kokoro ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.53,0:23:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There is one bright light, and with it a thousand souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.85,0:23:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,miageru sora wo shinjiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.85,0:23:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe in the sky above his head,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.26,0:23:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,michibiku hoshi wo higashi no takami ni sashishimesu yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.26,0:23:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,there putevodnaâ our star in the east, ee do not engage.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.18,0:23:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,yume wa kono te de kanaeru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.18,0:23:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And their cherished dream in flesh forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.74,0:24:01.80,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ナルサスは　ラジェンドラの性格の特異さを完全に見抜いている
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.93,0:24:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Narsus fully realized distinguishing trait Rajendra.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.46,0:24:06.10,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,自分自身をだますほどに　ラジェンドラは演技者なのだと
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.64,0:24:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He was such an actor that deceived even himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.76,0:24:09.04,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,次回　ふたたび河をこえて
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.94,0:24:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time: "Once again the river."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.67,0:24:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Chapter XVIII
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.44,0:24:12.01,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,少年は　そして王となる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.69,0:24:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the guy would be King.
